ax]","Example":"[40,120]","FilterMode":"[min,max]","Null":"YES","Key":"","Default":"","Extra":"","Comment":"抖音60秒以上视频CPM范围；固定写成[min,max]字符串"},{"Field":"kolOfficialPriceL1","Type":"varchar(255)","InputShape":"range-string [min,max]","Example":"[3000,10000]","FilterMode":"[min,max]","Null":"YES","Key":"","Default":"","Extra":"","Comment":"小红书图文或抖音1至20秒视频单达人官方报价范围；固定写成[min,max]字符串；三个报价字段至少一项为Brief业务必填"},{"Field":"kolOfficialPriceL2","Type":"varchar(255)","InputShape":"range-string [min,max]","Example":"[5000,15000]","FilterMode":"[min,max]","Null":"YES","Key":"","Default":"","Extra":"","Comment":"小红书视频或抖音21至60秒视频单达人官方报价范围；固定写成[min,max]字符串；三个报价字段至少一项为Brief业务必填"},{"Field":"kolOfficialPriceL3","Type":"varchar(255)","InputShape":"range-string [min,max]","Example":"[8000,20000]","FilterMode":"[min,max]","Null":"YES","Key":"","Default":"","Extra":"","Comment":"抖音60秒以上视频单达人官方报价范围；固定写成[min,max]字符串；三个报价字段至少一项为Brief业务必填"}]}
